Item (EN): Benefit Brow Contour Pro 4-In-1 Defining & Highlighting Brow Pencil "Blonde Light"
Description (EN):
What it is:

A 4-in-1 defining and highlighting brow pencil.

What it does:

Turn shapeless, flat brows into defined, contoured brows in an instant with this 4-in-1 contour pencil. It features a lighter brow shade, deeper brow shade, edge definer and arch highlighter to create clean, shaped brows with depth and dimension. It's available in five shades for a wide range of hair colours and skin tones.

What else you need to know:


Easy brow contouring
Blendable formula
24-hour longwear
Waterproof

 
HOW TO






Press down the lighter shade tab and twist until you see product and fill in the brow from start to arch. 

Press down the deeper shade tab and twist until you see product and fill in the brow from arch to end.

Stroke the definer below your brow from the start to end and above the brow from the arch to end and blend gently.

Apply the highlighter beneath your arch and blend outwards.
